{"tid":347071,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"行左好多間藥房,終於唔洗醫生紙買到支A酸,KETREL $98","createTime":"2017-08-04T13:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T12:52:45.000Z","uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"904c435dcb4c7c7926356e8fc471a69b3dff584f","tid":347071,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:05:03.000Z","msg":"之前有D藥房問我攞醫生紙先肯賣畀我,痴鳩線<br />\n呢D規矩都唔知邊D傻鳩定,益曬D醫療集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講返支藥,係響元朗X-LAND機鋪格離的藥房買,係第一代A酸黎,$98,好平<br />\n幾年前買過第三代A酸DIFFERIN GEL要$148,但越用覺得越無效,到後期轉用EPIDUO都覺得無乜效,所以想試下第一代<br />\n<br />\n支膏個樣係咁:<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/a3dIt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2Fa3dIt.jpg&h=344d5a28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢支濃度係0.05,有D牌子濃度係0.1,例如下面呢種,濃度高會比較易滲入真皮層<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.pacificpharm.com.hk/big5/products/product_detail/357/%E6%84%9B%E9%81%94%E7%BE%8E_ACTA_CREAM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pacificpharm.com.hk%2Fbig5%2Fproducts%2Fproduct_detail%2F357%2F%25E6%2584%259B%25E9%2581%2594%25E7%25BE%258E_ACTA_CREAM&d=jnb%2BnWhi%2FZlGGZHfiUG1DXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=9ac60f76\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.pacificpharm.com.hk/big5/products/product_detail/357/%E6%84%9B%E9%81%94%E7%BE%8E_ACTA_CREAM</a><br />\n<br />\n不過建議大家要用都係試左第三代A酸先,副作用同光敏性都比第一代少好多(但統計過第一二三代長期使用功效都係差唔多),相關資料自己GOOGLE下<br />\n<br />\n由於A酸有光敏性,所以我係日頭用SKINOREN,夜晚用A酸,交替使用,咁樣功效更好(純屬個人意見)"},{"pid":"1ea9c33f3e6102d7ffa081a8744327a4bdce534a","tid":347071,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:06:05.000Z","msg":"想問下樓主咁樣買犯唔犯法架"},{"pid":"0d4c51612ec62b81071ff772f3f906d28660bb26","tid":347071,"uid":18411,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:10:22.000Z","msg":"屌你，人地賣比你<br />\n你就放鳩人上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你同rose ma有乜撚嘢分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e154f0e33530eb7ec883e69741a908687f94223","tid":347071,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:13:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你，人地賣比你<br />\n你就放鳩人上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你同rose ma有乜撚嘢分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無開名,方便下其他病友啫,唔通乜鳩都叫人想知就PM咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ef6eb4f15e227904aab535c0516f8ab0bff30d","tid":347071,"uid":57110,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:13:46.000Z","msg":"白癡真係無藥醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人哋好心賣畀你就爆人出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58596cb24519646a8c06b5da8d085f7bc34f0784","tid":347071,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:14:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>白癡真係無藥醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人哋好心賣畀你就爆人出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爆你老母,收皮啦你"},{"pid":"6a513652e5af160aa5ed5216c5019768121b8729","tid":347071,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T14:02:29.000Z","msg":"支那毒菇走到來連登爆毒瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n